---
source: tests/contracts/causal_trace.rs
assertion: causal ledger commands use persisted evidence
schema:
  trace: ee.causal.trace.v1
  estimate: ee.causal.estimate.v1
  compare: ee.causal.compare.v1
  promote_plan: ee.causal.promote_plan.v1
contracts:
  - empty trace returns no generated chains
  - single-edge and branching ledgers produce deterministic chain IDs
  - cyclic ledgers are rejected before output
  - promotion creates a curation candidate with chain provenance
evidence:
  - causal_evidence.failure_id
  - causal_evidence.candidate_cause_id
  - causal_evidence.contribution_score
  - causal_evidence.evidence_uris_json
  - causal_evidence.method
